{"type": "article", "id": 10106, "title": "Nendo 新材料", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-28T07:24:35Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 20, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235529uCeFSZxabBfQXky9.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\tAlcantara 材料是意大利高端奢华材料品牌 Alcantara 的独家材料，因为其多样化的个性可能和高质量，用于时尚，家具，汽车等多个领域的设计和制造。最近，日本设计品牌 Nendo 对这种材料进行了全新演绎，他们把这些材料分层压紧并进行切片处理，营造出一种类似于年轮的的效果。形成的新的材料可以应用于家具，地板等制作。<a href=\"http://www.nendo.jp/\" target=\"_blank\">这是 Nendo 的主页</a>，点击可以查看他们更多作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016060523552669grjACnJUtoBKms.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052355268JaMAL45TK2jFQqg.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235527UzNoF1d9fGWJKrOT.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235527UHJXpm1hqrWl7Q0k.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235527AGLdCt3k1TZgQM2H.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235528AV90DFwmyYKNfEQR.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235528VQ0C8dfS7WhXD1e6.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}